rows.label: qst702410_msg0001
rows.name:
How is it? Did you find
any promising candidates?

rows.label: qst702410_msg0002
rows.name:
There must be some spirited and
cooperative people in the capital.

rows.label: qst702410_msg0003
rows.name:
If you find someone like
that, please talk to them.

rows.label: qst702410_msg0004
rows.name:
Also, we need six people,
but please talk to more than
that... about ten or so.

rows.label: qst702410_msg0005
rows.name:
Even if you find promising
candidates, not all of them
will necessarily volunteer.
